  "text": "Gene knockdown was performed using the pLKO vector (Addgene, 8453, Cambridge, MA, USA). The double-strand DNA oligo with shRNA sequence was inserted. The target sequences of shRNAs are listed in Supporting table S1. Knockdown cells were used 6 days after infection. For gene overexpression, pLenti 6.3 vector (Life Technologies, V533-06, Carlsbad, CA, USA) was used. The overexpression gene was cloned into the pENTR-FLAG vector [CITATION_1] , and subcloned into the pLenti 6.3 vector.",
